original_title: Rina Ellis Saves the World: A XXX 90's Parody
overview: When burnout slacker Rina Ellis greens out during a 90s movie marathon, she has some seriously fucked up dreams. Santanico Pandemonium has taken over an alternative 90s dystopia and it's up to Rina to save the day - if she wants to wake upm from her nightmare alive. Leelou, Lara Croft, and Xena help her stay alive... while penetrating as many holes as possible!
